to their YouTube channel, "the Crew Boyz" (yes the band has the same name as the au shush) which has around 200 subscribers.

the crew spends a lot of their time at the nearby ice cream parlor or skate park after school, or practicing their music in Karl's mom's basement, as it has thick walls and is near enough to the school for them to walk or skate to it.

Sapnap, Quackity, & Dream all go to the same hs that Karl & George graduated from. Karl is mostly chilling, trying to find a job + an apartment, ect. George is also trying to get moved out, but works as a teacher's assistant for the computer sciences program at their highschool.
